snippet.title: Chillingo presents...PREDATORS
snippet.description: Play as the Predator in this officially licensed game based on the latest chapter of the hit franchise PREDATORS™! Hone your hunting techniques to lethal precision as you earn full membership in the Predators clan by tracking down and eliminating packs of human killers, and defending yourself against even deadlier enemies...
